00:30:14,421 --> 00:30:17,554
YOU DON'T HAPPEN TO
KNOW ANY GHOST STORIES,
DO YOU, RUBE?

706
00:30:17,598 --> 00:30:20,644
UH, I'VE HEARD
A COUPLE IN MY DAY.OH, HOW FUN.

