714
00:30:39,881 --> 00:30:41,013
WHOO!

715
00:30:41,056 --> 00:30:42,884
[RECORD CONTINUES PLAYING]

716
00:30:42,928 --> 00:30:44,799
<i>♪ YOU TAKE
