00:42:41,297 --> 00:42:43,430
<i>THAT SHE WAS BORN
IN THE YEAR OF THE CAT,</i>

932
00:42:43,473 --> 00:42:46,346
<i>THAT SHE HAD ALL
THE QUALITIES OF A CAT.</i>

933
00:42:46,389 --> 00:42:48,696
<i>I SWEAR TO GOD,
IF SHE TOLD ME
SHE WENT IN A LITTER BOX,</i>

934
00:42:48,740 --> 00:42:50,568
<i>I WAS LEAVING HER
BY THE SIDE OF THE ROAD.</i>

935
00:42:51,569 --> 00:42:53,005
[DELORES]: ANYWAY...

936
00:43:00,665 --> 00:43:02,275
LOOKS GOOD.
MORE BUYERS COMING?

937
00:43:02,318 --> 00:43:04,320
NO. THIS IS FOR US.

938
00:43:04,364 --> 00:43:06,714
I THOUGHT WE DESERVED
A LITTLE SIT-DOWN
BREAKFAST.

939
00:43:06,758 --> 00:43:07,672
[CAR HORN HONKING]

940
00:43:08,629 --> 00:43:09,587
SORRY. I'VE GOT TO GO.

941
00:43:09,630 --> 00:43:10,805
OH, UH, WAIT.

942
00:43:10,849 --> 00:43:12,067
UM, HERE. TAKE BACON.

943
00:43:15,462 --> 00:43:16,985
YOU KNOW, REGGIE,

944
00:43:17,029 --> 00:43:18,813
IF YOU EVER WANT
TO TALK TO ME

945
00:43:18,857 --> 00:43:20,772
ABOUT ANYTHING,
YOU KNOW...

946
00:43:20,815 --> 00:43:22,425
I MEAN,
ANYTHING AT ALL,

947
00:43:22,469 --> 00:43:23,905
ABOUT GEORGE...

948
00:43:23,949 --> 00:43:25,211
[TELEPHONE RINGING]

949
00:43:30,346 --> 00:43:31,521
HELLO?

950
00:43:32,479 --> 00:43:33,219
HELLO?

951
00:43:34,742 --> 00:43:36,309
AW, COME ON.

952
00:43:36,352 --> 00:43:38,572
IF ANYONE IS THERE,
WOULD YOU JUST SAY
SOMETHING?

953
00:43:40,618 --> 00:43:41,880
FINE.

954
00:43:43,185 --> 00:43:44,099
YOU KNOW,
IF THAT KEEPS HAPPENING,

955
00:43:44,143 --> 00:43:46,058
I'M GOING TO CHANGE
OUR NUMBER.

956
00:43:46,101 --> 00:43:47,668
I DON'T THINK
THAT'S A GOOD IDEA.

957
00:43:47,712 --> 00:43:48,887
I'VE GOT TO GO.

958
00:43:49,844 --> 00:43:54,153
[DOOR OPENS, CLOSES]

959
00:43:56,459 --> 00:43:57,722
[CAR ENGINE STARTING]

960
00:44:32,278 --> 00:44:36,108
[GEORGE]:  <i>ONCE UPON A TIME,
THERE WAS A GIRL NAMED GEORGE,</i>

961
00:44:36,151 --> 00:44:39,285
<i>WHO COULDN'T QUITE FORGET
THERE WAS ONCE UPON A TIME.</i>

962
00:44:42,070 --> 00:44:43,681
[♪♪]

